    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline via eight individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp 7-speed M-DCT, the drivetrain remains tight with consistent engagement and rapid shift points. The chassis benefits from high-precision hydraulic steering and an active M Variable Differential Lock for superior lateral dynamics. Recently serviced with a focus on preventative maintenance, the suspension bushings and subframe mounts are in solid order. A driver-focused example that balances mechanical purity with daily usability.",
