    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s looking for a great new home. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been super reliable for me\u2014always kept tidy and runs beautifully. It\u2019s a fantastic ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today! If you're looking for something dependable that still looks sharp, this is the one for you. I've loved driving this beauty, and I'm sure you will too. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
