    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sound E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power unit features eight individual throttle bodies and a sophisticated VANOS variable valve timing system, delivering a linear power curve up to an 8,300 RPM redline. The vehicle features a crisp M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a variable M differential lock for superior torque vectoring. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the structural integrity of the rotating assembly. The suspension maintains factory-spec geometry, providing the communicative steering feel and lateral stability expected of the M-chassis. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals remain robust, offering a visceral, high-performance driving experience for the discerning purist.",
